reviewText: Product does not work.  Do not buy this!!!!!!!!

This was embarrassing. I can't even begin to tell you how ashamed i am that i spent money on this at all.  It looks as though someone recorded and tried to edit it in their living room. By far the worst thing I've ever spent money on. DO NOT WASTE YOUR TIME AND MONEY>> I'm not even going to return it because apparently someone needs the money, SORRY HORRIBLE PLEASE DONT DO IT!

DO NOT BUY THIS DVD!!! I can not believe someone would have the nerve to sell this video.  I have never posted a review on any site, but was prompted to after watching less than 2 minutes of this dvd.  Not worth sending it back. Threw it away -
